    "type": "p",
    "style": "743",
    "text": "概述"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "744",
    "text": "系统位置"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "",
    "text": "RguGCtrl含有两个模块，分别是GlbCtrl(global control)和ClusCtrl(cluster control)模块，其在系统中的位置如下图所示。一方面，GlbCtrl模块和系统外通过axi-lite交互，用于获取kernel参数配置；另一方面，ClusCtrl模块和系统内的Control Fabric(ctrl noc)通过axi-lite相连，把参数发给各个core。"
  },
  {
    "type": "image",
    "rid": "rId11",
    "target": "media/image1.png",
    "seq": 1
  },
  {
    "type": "image",
    "rid": "rId12",
    "target": "media/image2.png",
    "seq": 2
  },
  {
    "type": "image",
    "rid": "rId11",
    "target": "media/image1.png",
    "seq": 3
  },
  {
    "type": "image",
    "rid": "rId12",
    "target": "media/image2.png",
    "seq": 4
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "",
    "text": "图1"
  },
  {
    "type": "image",
    "rid": "rId11",
    "target": "media/image1.png",
    "seq": 5
  },
  {
    "type": "image",
    "rid": "rId11",
    "target": "media/image1.png",
    "seq": 6
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "",
    "text": "每个die含有一个GlbCtrl模块，连接CP(kernel dispatch)和ctrl noc，每个die独立运行；physical cluster则共有CLUS_N个，每个physical cluster内含有一个ClusCtrl模块和CORE_N个core。"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "744",
    "text": "功能列表"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "",
    "text": "RguGCtrl模块的功能有："
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "774",
    "text": "将kernel的参数配置reg info拆分为logic cluster；将regi nfo和logic cluster通过Router分发给CLUS_N个physical cluster中的一个或多个，分发方式支持random和fixed两大类"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "774",
    "text": "将logic cluster拆分为block，并将reg info和blocks通过全互联reg总线分发给CLCR_N个core中的一个或多个"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "774",
    "text": "支持同时处理多个kernel；多个kernel可以并行执行，占用不同的physical cluster；每个physical cluster只能同时执行1个kernel"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "774",
    "text": "上报debug信息和中断等（TODO）"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "743",
    "text": "整体架构"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "",
    "text": "整体架构图参考图1，简要图如图2所示，RguGCtrl主要包括2个子模块，GlbCtrl和ClusCtrl。其中蓝线是Router，红线是全互联。"
  },
  {
    "type": "image",
    "rid": "rId13",
    "target": "media/image3.png",
    "seq": 7
  },
  {
    "type": "image",
    "rid": "rId13",
    "target": "media/image3.png",
    "seq": 8
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "",
    "text": "图2"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "",
    "text": "GlbCtrl模块功能如下："
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "774",
    "text": "通过axilite接口接收kernel配置信息reg info，支持缓存最多KNEL_N个kernel的信息；按序调度kernel，kernel packet寄存器被读出后，只要剩余的cluster资源满足下一个kernel的使用，就可以进行下一个kernel的调度，kernel所对应的cluster index发送完成后，则可清空该kernel的packet寄存器，从cp接收新的kernel packet；每个physical cluster只能同时执行1个kernel"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "774",
    "text": "根据griddim / clusdim / ctanum / cluster status等信息，自动给kernel分配需要的physical cluster，也支持直接配置"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "774",
    "text": "生成cluster mask，并将其与数据、地址合并成一笔数据，经axilite接口通过Router进行传输，Router根据cluster mask将reg info发送给对应的physical cluster"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "774",
    "text": "将kernel拆分为logic cluster，并逐个发给选中的每个physical cluster。支持随机分配和固定分配两种模式，随机分配选择最空闲的physical分配，固定分配则需要分配到特定的physical cluster"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "774",
    "text": "kernel分配过程中有physical cluster释放时，若该kernel已使用的physical cluster数尚未达到分配值，可以选中其进行reg info和logic cluster的分配"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "774",
    "text": "通过axilite接口给Router发送配置"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "774",
    "text": "通过axilite接口接收core的上报信息，维护各个physical cluster内logic cluster的执行情况。kernel的所有logic cluster都完成后，生成kernel_done信号，并将对应的kernel index上报给cp"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "",
    "text": "ClusCtrl模块功能如下："
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "774",
    "text": "通过包接口(vld/data/ready)接收配置信息"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "774",
    "text": "通过内部全互联接口把reg info广播给physical cluster内所有的core"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "774",
    "text": "将logic cluster拆分为block，按照最空闲的顺序逐一发给每个core。需要同时发送cluster index和block index"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "774",
    "text": "通过内部全互联接口，接收来自core的上报信息，维护各个core内block的执行情况"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "style": "774",
    "text": "通过包接口(vld/data/ready)给Router上报cluster的执行情况"
  },
